{"tid":2224134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Part time騙\b案?","createTime":"2020-09-30T09:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T10:18:31.000Z","uid":371256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e56004f3c560f7614a67de3d83da4c9fa1365a38","tid":2224134,"uid":371256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:59:59.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n<br />\n小弟從未申請過 part time <br />\n但就近幾年都間唔中有人打來話我apply左<br />\n<br />\n上網搵見有人話係垃圾電話呃人見工sell保險<br />\n但係一來公司唔同 二來佢地又神奇地叫得出我個姓<br />\n老老豆豆我又唔係陳李張黃何啲大路姓<br />\n好明顯係真係有我資料<br />\n<br />\n試過叫佢地幫我取消 不過諗下都知一定唔會有用<br />\n因為佢地都唔知經幾多手先拎到我啲資料 <br />\n有無人都遇過 知究竟係咩事 同係咪已經搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0240fa017e42470f40a72dc897b7c85756294b93","tid":2224134,"uid":371256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:15:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cafb4b791880a88671d6bbfbe37a2c19f9d08ffd","tid":2224134,"uid":57671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:18:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}